                    <tr>
                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> You can kill them before 34, but the split is very tricky and needs a good deal of luck.  At 34, with Invoke Fear, the split is probably the hardest thing you have had to do, but isn't really difficult.<br /><br />You don't need to snare the first one you fear away.  Let him run.  Also, my pet was never snared; often rooted, but never snared.  You want to kill the first one quickly, and the second slowly, so as to make a good split.  So burn your mana on the first ranger, and keep the second one feared away.  He will come back, no matter how far he runs.<br /></span id="msg"></font></td>
                    </tr>
